OL,3,CAll still to play for ` Arsenal
OL,4,Ccaptain defiant despite defeat to Man
OL,5,CCity
OL,7,FArsenal captain Martin Odegaard
OL,8,Finsists it is still "all to play for"
OL,9,Fdespite rivals Manchester City taking
OL,10,Fcharge of the Premier League title
OL,11,Frace.
OL,13,FThe Gunners are on the brink of being
OL,14,Fdisplaced at the top of the table
OL,15,Ffollowing their 2-1 defeat to Pep
OL,16,FGuardiola's side at the Etihad Stadium.
OL,18,FA victory for City against Burnley at
OL,19,FTurf Moor on Wednesday would end
OL,20,FArsenal's 200-day reign at the summit
OL,21,Fwith just five matches to play.
OL,26,@pD@UOUpD@eO]
