PN,40802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1776780668
OL,3,CAll still to play for ` Arsenal
OL,4,Ccaptain defiant despite defeat to Man
OL,5,CCity
OL,7,FHowever, even if City win, Arsenal
OL,8,Fwill still be level on points ` and
OL,9,FOdegaard has urged his team-mates to
OL,10,Fdeliver a much-needed victory in their
OL,11,Fnext match against Newcastle at the
OL,12,FEmirates Stadium on Saturday.
OL,14,F"We have to keep going," said
OL,15,FOdegaard. "It was always going to go
OL,16,Fall the way to the end so we have to
OL,17,Fkeep going, keep working hard and
OL,18,Fsticking together.
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@XO]wD@KOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1776780668
OL,3,CAll still to play for ` Arsenal
OL,4,Ccaptain defiant despite defeat to Man
OL,5,CCity
OL,7,F"We just look forward to the next game
OL,8,Fnow and bounce back. We created a few
OL,9,Fbig, big chances (against City) so
OL,10,Fthere are some positives to take.
OL,12,F"It is frustrating at the moment but
OL,13,Fwe'll analyse it, move onto the next
OL,14,Fone, and it's all to play for. This is
OL,15,Fthe best part of the season so we will
OL,16,Fjust look forward to the next game."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUxD@dO]
