OL,3,CAll still to play for ` Arsenal
OL,4,Ccaptain defiant despite defeat to Man
OL,5,CCity
OL,7,FArsenal's defeat on Sunday was their
OL,8,Ffourth in a row on the domestic stage
OL,9,Fafter their loss in the Carabao Cup
OL,10,Ffinal, also to City, was followed by a
OL,11,Fshock FA Cup exit against Southampton.
OL,13,FA crushing home defeat to Bournemouth
OL,14,Fensued, with Arteta's men only playing
OL,15,Fto the narrative of "bottling" their
OL,16,Ftrophy ambitions as the season reaches
OL,17,Fits climax.
OL,26,@wD@UOUwD@^O]
