OL,3,CAll still to play for ` Arsenal
OL,4,Ccaptain defiant despite defeat to Man
OL,5,CCity
OL,7,FShould City see off Burnley, a home
OL,8,Fmatch against Eddie Howe's struggling
OL,9,FNewcastle will present Arsenal with a
OL,10,Fchance to move back ahead of their
OL,11,Ftitle rivals who will be in FA Cup
OL,12,Fsemi-final action this weekend.
OL,14,FHowever, the Emirates has been riddled
OL,15,Fwith anxiety for much of the calendar
OL,16,Fyear, and Arsenal were subjected to
OL,17,Fboos by some of the crowd after their
OL,18,Floss against the Cherries.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/6
